ActNational Capital Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Employment and Social Development of LISA MACDONALD of New Glasgow, Nova Scotia, to be a member of the Board of Directors of the National Capital Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Jason Michael Sordi, effective July 1, 2015.
